text: Woh Apna Sa is an Indian Hindi-Language television soap opera. Which premiered on 23 January 2017. And is broadcast on Zee TV. The show will be produced by Rashmi Sharma Telefilms Limited. It Stars Disha Panwar,Sudeep Sahir and Manasi Salvi. The show follows the story of Jhanvi and Arjun True Love.Ridhi Dogra who initially played the antagonist role of Nisha quit the show and wswas later replaced by Manasi Salvi. It previously aired Mon-Fri 10PM, but now airs Mon-Fri 7PM as Ishq Subhan Allah was given the 10PM timeslot ==Cast== ===Main=== * Disha Parmar as Jia Aakash Khanna/Jhanvi Aditya Jindal * Sudeep Sahir as Arjun Khanna/Aditya Jindal * Tanya Sharma as Binni Jindal * Sara Khan as Rano Arjun Khanna * Manasi Salvi as Nisha Samar Sukhla *Swasti Katyal as Chinni Aditya Jindal *Reyhna Malhotra as Tamara *Ashish Kapoor as Samar Sukhla * Alka Kausal as Ambika Khanna ===Recurring=== *Ushma Rathod as Sharda Darmesh Jindal * Isha Anand Sharma As Doctor Priya *Buneet Kapoor as Raj Jindal *Amit Behl as Dharmesh Jindal *Ananya Khare as Sudha *Sabina Jat as Surbhi Agarwal ==References== Category:2017 Indian television series debuts Category:Hindi- language television series
